at</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tactical team-based gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visceral and immersive firefights</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Near-future city setting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vertical urban environments </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Community-driven development</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Regular updates and improvements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique handcrafted gun sounds </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vast arsenal</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple sides of the conflict </p></li></ul>",
